(14, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-properties-for-sale', 'Discover Bulgarian Property for Sale | Latest properties | Yantra Homes', 'bulgarian property for sale, bulgarian properties for sale, bulgarian property, bulgaria property for sale', 'Looking for Bulgarian property for sale? Find your dream house or apartment in Bulgaria with our extensive listings. All available to buy now!', 'Bulgarian property for sale - You can find your dream home in Bulgaria with our extensive listings. All available to buy now!', '<h2>If you are searching for the Bulgarian property of your dreams?<br/> The next two pages cover our Latest listings</h2><br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Our agency is pleased to present our latest listings of Bulgarian property for sale. If you\'re searching for a great place to invest in real estate, Bulgaria is definitely worth considering. With affordable prices and a growing number of tourists visiting the country every year, it\'s no wonder that more and more foreign buyers and investors are taking notice.\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Bulgarian property for sale</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Bulgarian property for sale &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">\r\n\r\nThe region that we highly recommend checking out is Veliko Tarnovo. Located in central Bulgaria, this area boasts stunning mountain views and plenty of historical landmarks. Whether you\'re interested in buying a traditional Bulgarian home or an apartment in the city center, there\'s something here for everyone.<br/><br/>\r\nAnother region that\'s worth exploring is Gabrovo. Situated at the foot of the Balkan Mountains, this area offers plenty of opportunities for outdoor activities like hiking, skiing, and fishing. Plus, with its charming small towns and villages, it\'s easy to find a peaceful retreat away from the hustle and bustle of city life.\r\n<h2>Bulgarian Real Estate</h2>\r\nOf course, one of the biggest draws of Bulgarian property for sale is the affordable prices. Compared to other European countries like France or Spain, you can get much more bang for your buck here. And with so many different types of properties available - from houses to apartments to commercial spaces - there\'s no shortage of options.<br/><br/>\r\nBut perhaps what makes Bulgaria such an attractive option for foreign buyers and investors is its growing tourism industry. In recent years, more and more people have been flocking to this beautiful country to explore its rich history and culture. And as demand continues to rise, so too does the potential value of your investment.\r\n<h2>Apartments and Houses in Beautiful Bulgarian Locations</h2>\r\nSo if you\'re looking for a great place to buy property abroad, look no further than Bulgaria! With our latest listings covering everything from village properties to modern city apartments, we\'re confident that you\'ll find exactly what you\'re looking for with us.<br/><br/>\r\nThere\'s no shortage of options. From quaint countryside cottages to modern city apartments, there\'s something here for every taste and budget. And with our expert team on hand to guide you through the buying process, you can rest assured that you\'ll find exactly what you are searching for.\r\n<h2>Yantra Homes: Top Choice for Bulgarian Properties for Sale</h2>\r\nYantra Homes is a company that offers some of the best Bulgarian properties for sale. The company specialises in town and village properties, providing buyers with access to some of the most beautiful locations in Bulgaria. Whether you are looking for an apartment in the city or a house in the countryside, Yantra Homes has something for everyone.\r\n<h2>Town and Village Properties</h2>\r\nThe company\'s focus on quality and customer satisfaction makes it a top choice for anyone looking to invest in Bulgarian real estate. With a wide range of properties available, including apartments and houses, foreign buyers can easily find their dream home in Bulgaria.\r\n<h2>Bulgarian property for sale - Veliko Tarnovo Region</h2>\r\n<h2>Affordable Bulgarian Properties for Sale in Veliko Tarnovo Region</h2>\r\n<h2>Mountain Views and Cultural Hub</h2>\r\nThe Veliko Tarnovo Region in Bulgaria is a hidden gem that offers affordable Bulgarian properties for sale. Located in the heart of Bulgaria, this region boasts stunning mountain views and a rich cultural history. The region is home to the famous Tsarevets Fortress, which has stood for centuries as a symbol of Bulgaria\'s strength and resilience.<br/><br/>\r\nOn this page you will find examples of properties offered by Yantra Homes, located in Veliko Tarnovo - one of Bulgaria\'s most beautiful cities. These properties are perfect for those who want to enjoy all that this historic city has to offer while still being able to retreat to their own private oasis at any time.\r\n<h2>Bulgarian property for sale - Gabrovo Region</h2>\r\nOther properties offered by Yantra Homes include the region of Gabrovo - a charming town known as \"the Bulgarian capital of humor.\" Properties in the villages nearby offers stunning views of the surrounding mountains and countryside while still being close enough to all amenities.\r\n<h2>Outdoor Activities Galore</h2>\r\nApart from its scenic beauty, Gabrovo Region also offers a range of outdoor activities such as hiking, fishing, and horseback riding. With miles of unspoiled countryside to explore, it\'s no wonder why tourists flock to this area year after year. Whether you\'re an adrenaline junkie or just looking for some peace and quiet away from the hustle and bustle of city life, Gabrovo Region is the perfect place to unwind and relax.\r\n<h2>Customer Satisfaction</h2>\r\nAt Yantra Homes, customer satisfaction is key. The company understands that buying a property can be stressful, especially if you are doing so from another country. That\'s why they provide excellent customer service throughout every step of the process.<br/><br/>\r\nFor example, when you first contact Yantra Homes about purchasing a property, they will take the time to understand your needs and preferences before recommending suitable options. They will then guide you through every step of the buying process, from arranging viewings to completing all necessary paperwork.\r\n<h2>Real Estate Opportunities</h2>\r\nInvesting in Bulgarian property can be a smart financial move, as property values have been steadily increasing over the past few years. With low prices and high potential returns on investment, now is an excellent time to consider purchasing real estate in Veliko Tarnovo.\r\n<h2>Bulgaria: An Attractive Destination for Foreign Property Buyers</h2>\r\nOne of the main reasons Bulgaria is so popular among foreign property buyers is Bulgaria\'s low cost of living and favourable tax laws. Compared to other European countries like France or Spain, Bulgaria is significantly cheaper in terms of real estate prices and general living expenses. This makes it an attractive option for those who want to invest in a second home without breaking the bank.\r\n<h2>Real Estate Market Outlook</h2>\r\nThe Bulgarian property market has been steadily growing over the past few years. According to data from the National Statistical Institute (NSI), there was a 5% increase in property sales in 2020 compared to 2019, despite the COVID-19 pandemic. This shows that despite economic uncertainty caused by the pandemic, people are still interested in investing in Bulgarian properties.\r\n<h2>Why Choose Yantra Homes for Bulgarian property for sale?</h2>\r\n<h2>Yantra Homes: The Best Choice for Bulgarian Property for Sale</h2>\r\n<h2>12 Years of Experience</h2>\r\nThere are countless real estate agencies to choose from. However, one agency stands out among the rest: Yantra Homes. With over 12 years of experience in the industry, Yantra Homes has established itself as a leading real estate agency in Bulgaria.\r\n<h2>Wide Range of Properties</h2>\r\nOne of the main reasons why Yantra Homes is such a popular choice among buyers is because they offer a wide range of properties for sale in Bulgaria. Whether you\'re looking for an apartment in Veliko Tarnovo or a villa in the Mountains aroud Gabrovo, Yantra Homes has something to suit every taste and budget.\r\n<h2>Excellent Customer Service</h2>\r\nAt Yantra Homes, customer service is always a top priority. Their team of multilingual professionals provides exceptional service to clients from all over the world. From your initial inquiry right through to completion of your purchase, you can expect nothing but the best from Yantra Homes.\r\n<h2>Expert Advice</h2>\r\nAnother reason why so many buyers choose Yantra Homes is because they have a deep understanding of the Bulgarian property market. Their team can provide expert advice on everything from legal requirements to local customs and culture. This level of expertise ensures that you make an informed decision when buying property in Bulgaria.\r\n<h2>Competitive Prices and Transparent Transactions</h2>\r\nFinally, at Yantra Homes, you can expect competitive prices and transparent transactions. They understand that buying property is a significant investment and strive to ensure that the process is as hassle-free as possible. With their help, you can rest assured that your purchase will be handled professionally and efficiently.\r\n<h2>Begin your Bulgarian property search with Yantra Homes today</h2>\r\nIf you\'re looking for a stunning countryside property, our selection of property in the Veliko Tarnovo region will not disappoint. From traditional Bulgarian homes to modern villas with breathtaking views, we have something for everyone. The region also boasts a variety of properties, including renovated townhouses and spacious apartments.<br/><br/>\r\nWhether you\'re looking for a holiday home or an investment property, Yantra Homes has something for everyone. So why wait? Begin your Bulgarian property search with us today and start living your dream life in this beautiful country.\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Bulgarian property</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Bulgarian properties for sale - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-properties-for-sale/page-1', 'Desktop'),
