(43, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'traditional-houses-for-sale', 'Traditional Bulgarian Houses for Sale | Yantra Homes', 'traditional bulgarian houses, traditional bulgarian house for sale,traditional house for sale in bulgaria , bulgarian traditional houses, traditional houses for sale in bulgaria, traditional style Bulgarian houses', 'Discover a range of traditional Bulgarian houses for sale in Veliko Tarnovo, the ancient capital of Bulgaria. Yantra Homes offers a wide range of options to choose from, each property rich in history and constructed using traditional materials.', 'Traditional Bulgarian Houses for Sale in Veliko Tarnovo', '<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Are you looking to invest in a property that takes you back in time? Yantra Homes has got you covered! We offer a range of traditional Bulgarian houses for sale in and around Veliko Tarnovo, the ancient capital of Bulgaria. These properties are rich in history and have been constructed using traditional materials like stone and wood.<br/>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>traditional Bulgarian houses for sale</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Bulgarian traditional properties for sale &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">\r\n\r\n<h2>Traditional Bulgarian Houses: A Timeless Investment</h2>\r\nOwning a traditional Bulgarian house is not just an investment in property, but an investment in history and Bulgarian culture. The traditional style of construction for Bulgarian houses is with stone and wood, which has been practiced for centuries. These houses are buil