ations throughout the country. From the stunning mountain ranges in the north to the picturesque countryside in the south, we have something to suit every taste and budget.<br/>\r\nEach of our properties is unique, with its own special charm and character. Our listings include cottages, farmhouses, and family homes, all of which have been carefully selected for their quality and authenticity. Whether you are looking for a property to renovate or a move-in ready home, we have something to suit your needs.\r\n\r\n<h2>The Region Covered by Yantra Homes</h2>\r\nVeliko Tarnovo is a city steeped in history and culture. It was the capital of the Second Bulgarian Empire and is home to some of the most impressive historical landmarks in the country. Yantra Homes covers the entire region of Veliko Tarnovo and offers a range of traditional properties for sale.\r\n\r\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\r\nIf you are looking for a unique and charming property in Bulgaria, look no further than Yantra Homes\' listings of traditional Bulgarian houses for sale. Our selection of properties showcases the traditional style of construction with stone and wood, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere for you to call home. With our team of experienced agents by your side, we can help you find the perfect property to suit your needs and budget.<br/>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>traditional Bulgarian properties</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Traditional Bulgarian property for sale - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/traditional-houses-for-sale/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(44, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'luxury-houses-for-sale', 'Luxury Bulgarian Properties for Sale - Find Your Perfect Fit | Yantra Homes', 'bulgarian property for sale', 'Searching for Bulgarian property? Look no further! Our top selection of luxury properties offers the perfect fit for any buyer.', 'Luxury Bulgarian Properties for Sale - Which One is Right for You?', '<h1>Looking for a property to call your own in Bulgaria?</h1>\r\n	<p>From luxurious apartments to grandiose villas, check out our top selection of homes for sale. Find the perfect fit that suits your needs and budget – right here!</p>\r\n	<h2>Identify Your Budget.</h2>\r\n	<p>Before beginning your search, it’s important to identify a budget that works for you. This will make the process of searching and selecting the perfect property much easier and ensure that you only view homes within your range. Make sure to factor in any additional costs such as transfer fees, legal fees and stamp duties when deciding on an appropriate budget for your Bulgarian home.</p>\r\n	<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\">\r\n		<span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Luxury Property</strong></span>\r\n		<img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Bulgarian Property &ndash; Read More\" />\r\n	</span>\r\n	<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify\" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">\r\n		<h2>Set Your Priorities & Goals.</h2>\r\n		<p>Buying a home is an emotional decision as much as it is a practical one. Before beginning to search for your Bulgarian property, take the time to sit down and assess your priorities and goals. Consider what type of lifestyle you are looking for—would you prefer living in the city or countryside? Do you have any other needs such as proximity to amenities and schools that must be incorporated? Knowing what type of property you’re after will make it easier to find the perfect fit.</p>\r\n		<h2>Determine What Kind of Property You Prefer.</h2>\r\n		<p>Whether you are looking for a luxury mountain retreat, an urban city apartment, or something in between—decide what kind of property suits you best. Do you want to buy a house to renovate and make your own? Or would you prefer something that is already updated and ready to move into? Keep in mind that purchasing land offers a different set of challenges than purchasing a pre-existing structure. Knowing which works best for your situation will help narrow down the list of potential properties.</p>\r\n		<br />\r\n		<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\">\r\n			<span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Luxury Property</strong></span>\r\n			<img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Property in Bulgaria - Hide\" />\r\n		</span>\r\n	</div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/luxury-houses-for-sale/page-1', 'Desktop'),
