(80, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'commercial-property-vt-region', 'Commercial Property For Sale in Veliko Tarnovo Region | Yantra Homes', 'Bulgaria Veliko Tarnovo, commercial properties for sale Veliko Tarnovo ', 'Veliko Tarnovo is uniquely located in the centre of Bulgaria and perfectly positioned for trade and commerce throughout Europe into Asia. We have commercial properties throughout the region for investors looking to capitalise on the area\'s location  ', 'Commercial Property For Sale in Veliko Tarnovo Region', '<p>Strategically located in the centre of Bulgaria Veliko Tarnovo is a town perfectly positioned for commerce and trade in Bulgaria and the rest of Europe.&nbsp; We have new and resale commercial properties for sale in the Veliko Tarnovo region for investors, entrepreneurs and businesspeople wishing to capitalise on the area\'s unique location.</p>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/commercial-property-vt-region/page-1', 'Desktop'),
