(107, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'large-regulated-building-plots', 'Bulgarian Land for Sale - Large regulated plots | Yantra Homes', 'regulated land in Bulgaria for sale, land in regulation in Bulgaria', 'large regulated plots of land for sale in various location throughout the Veliko Tarnovo region for new home builds, campsites, hotel complexes or gas stations', 'Large Regulated Building Plots For Sale in Bulgaria', '<p>Large plots of regulated land in Bulgaria for sale in various prime locations throughout the region. Suitable for building a home, large property developments, campsites, hotel complexes, restaurants or petrol stations, many of these plots have access to water, electricity and roads.&nbsp; Land in regulation in Bulgaria is a great investment as the right to develop has already been granted by the government</p>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/large-regulated-building-plots/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(108, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'agricultural-land', 'Bulgaria Land Agricultural & Unregulated Plots for Sale | Yantra Homes', 'Bulgaria unregulated land, investment in Bulgaria, Bulgaria buy unregulated or agricultural land', 'Buy agricultural land out of regulation in great locations for future development once it has been regulated and planning permission granted', 'Agricultural & Unregulated Land For Sale in Bulgaria', '<p>In Bulgaria \'unregulated\' land is agricultural land that would require &lsquo;regulating&rsquo; before construction of any kind can take place. This process takes time and money, but if you are looking for a cheap and easy investment in Bulgaria buy unregulated or agricultural land in prime locations, near roads, electricity and water, with south facing or mountain views for future development and where you can be sure to obtain planning permission&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/agricultural-land/page-1', 'Desktop'),
