(187, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-malki-chiflik', 'Property in Malki Chiflik - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Malki Chiflik property for sale, buy properties in Malki Chiflik', 'Property in Malki Chiflik - All the latest properties for sale in Malki Chiflik | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Malki Chiflik - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Malki Chiflik &ndash; The closest village to Veliko Tarnovo</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Malki Chiflik benefits from being a \"suburb&rdquo; of Veliko Tarnovo and literally translated means \"Little Homestead\" or \"Little Farm\".<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Malki Chiflik property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Malki Chiflik, Malko Chiflik, Malki Chiflick, Malko Chiflick, Малки Чифлик</strong><br /><br /> The area comprises of wooded hills that provide scenic views from most of the houses in <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong>, and panoramic views to the valley of the River Yantra and Veliko Tarnovo nestling in the valley. The region is rich with historical and cultural locations including monasteries, churches and eco-trails situated nearby. It offers an ideal location for relaxing and yet is only a hop from the town. <br /><br /> <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong> was founded after the fall of Veliko Tarnovo and the surrounding area under the Ottoman Empire. The most famous site in the village is Troshana, named after a local Boyar (Nobleman or Aristocrat) who farmed there and hence where the name of the village likely originated from. Wealthy Bulgarians settled thereafter and in 1878 it was declared a village, with most plots in <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong> having scenic views and commanding higher prices than the norm. <br /><br /> Today <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong> is very peaceful with both Bulgarian and foreign nationals making it their permanent place of residence in some beautifully restored revival style houses in <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong>.  There is a local and well stocked shop, cafe and bar with regular public transport to Veliko Tarnovo or a very low fare in a taxi. <br /><br /> Please find below, a full list of the latest Property for sale in <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong><br /><br /> Nearest towns &ndash; Veliko Tarnovo 5km, Lyaskovets 8km<br /> Nearest villages - Shemshevo 3km, Arbanasi 6km<br /> Altitude: 200 - 299m above sea level<br /> Area size of Village of <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong>: 6.015km2<br /> Post code: 5028 Latitude: 43.067N Longitude: 25.683E<br /> <span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Malki Chiflik</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Malki Chiflik - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-malki-chiflik/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(188, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-kilifarevo', 'Property in Kilifarevo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Kilifarevo property for sale, buy properties in Kilifarevo', 'Property in Kilifarevo - All the latest properties for sale in Kilifarevo | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Kilifarevo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The town of Kilifarevo can provide everything for everyday living.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\"><br /><strong>Kilifarevo</strong> is a small town of around 2500 inhabitants just 10km south of Veliko Tarnovo. Once a village, <strong>Kilifarevo</strong> was declared a town in 1973.\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about Kilifarevo</span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Kilifarevo property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">The town provides good local amenities with a selection of shops, bars, restaurants and cafes.  There is also a school, community centre and museum. It also has an excellent modern sports complex offering swimming and tennis, bar and restaurant. There is good public transport service as well as satellite/internet/mobile coverage. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\nIn a forest beside the Belitsa River, 4km outside the town lays <strong>Kilifarevo</strong> monastery. Built in 1718, just above the old monastery, it was converted into a convent in 1950. Also in the area are remains of ancient Thracian civilization including the ruins of a fortress which guarded a pass through the Balkan Mountains during the time of the Roman Empire.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nNearest Towns:  Veliko Tarnovo -10km, Debelets – 5km<br/>\r\nNearest Village:  Natsovtsi – 3km, Yalovo-5km<br/>\r\nPlaces of Interest:  <strong>Kilifarevo</strong> monastery, Saint Archangel Michael Church<br/>\r\nAltitude: 200 - 299 m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea size of <strong>Kilifarevo</strong>: 28 km2<br/>\r\nPost code: 5050<br/>\r\nLatitude: 42.983N  Longitude: 25.633E<br/>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Kilifarevo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Kilifarevo - Hide\" /> </span></div>\r\n', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-kilifarevo/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(189, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-kapinovo', 'Property in Kapinovo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Kapinovo property for sale, buy properties in Kapinovo', 'Property in Kapinovo - All the latest properties for sale in Kapinovo | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Kapinovo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Kapinovo &ndash; Veliko Tarnovo Municipality</p>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-kapinovo/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(190, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-plakovo', 'Property in Plakovo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Plakovo property for sale, buy properties in Plakovo', 'Property in Plakovo - All the latest properties for sale in Plakovo | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Plakovo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The village of Plakovo is set in a wonderfully rural location offering great views of the Elena Balkan hills.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\"><br />The village of <strong>Plakovo</strong> lies 15km due south from Veliko Tarnovo and can be reached on route 551 toward Elena via the town of Debelets.\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about Plakovo</span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Plakovo property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Plakovo</strong> is a well developed village with around 250 inhabitants and offers the basic amenities required for everyday living including grocery shops, 2 bars, Post Office and medical facilities 3 days a week. The road through the village is excellent and there is a regular bus service to Veliko Tarnovo and neighboring villages available. <strong>Plakovo</strong> is close to 2 dams.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nTwo kilometers out of the village is the Plakovski Monastery which has been declared a monument of culture. It was rebuilt after Turkish rule in 1845, the great Bulgarian builder Kolyu Ficheto adding a magnificent 26 metre bell tower, complete with beautiful decorative masonry, a stone fountain and residential buildings in 1865. The residential buildings were destroyed by fire in 1949.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nNearest Towns: Veliko Tarnovo – 15km, Elena – 23.9km, Debelets – 10.6km, Kilifaravo 5.8km<br/>\r\nNearest Village: Golemanite – 4 km, Malchovtsi – 4 km<br/>\r\nPlaces of interest: Plakovski Monastery<br/>\r\nCoordinates: 42.967N, 25.683E<br/>\r\nAltitude:  from 200 to 299 above sea level<br/>\r\nArea Size: 29.841km2<br/>\r\nPostal Code: 5042<br/>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Plakovo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Plakovo - Hide\" /> </span></div>\r\n', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-plakovo/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(191, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-pchelishte', 'Property in Pchelishte - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Pchelishte property for sale, buy properties in Pchelishte', 'Property in Pchelishte - All the latest properties for sale in Pchelishte | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Pchelishte - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The village of Pchelishte lies in a valley surrounded by wooded hills and fields and is great for walking and exploring the area.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\"><br /><strong>Pchelishte</strong> is a small village of around 33km2 with a population of approximately 600 inhabitants just 12km from the old Bulgarian capital, Veliko Tarnovo.\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about Pchelishte</span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Pchelishte property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Its close proximity to Veliko Tarnovo makes <strong>Pchelishte</strong> one of the most popular villages in the area for Bulgarians and foreigners alike because they can easily enjoy both town and country life.  The village has its own church Assumption of the Virgin Orthodox Church, where some outstandingly beautiful hand painted icons have been lovingly restored.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nVillage amenities include grocery shops, bars and cafes. A Medical centre, community centre, post office and kindergarten.  There is a regular bus service to town and neighboring villages, good roads and excellent internet/satellite/mobile reception. There are some wonderful views to the distant Elena Balkan mountains and the area is renowned for its honey.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nNearest Town:  Veliko Tarnovo – 12km, Debelets – 9km<br/>\r\nNearest Villages:  Prisovo – 4km, Tserova koriya – 2km   Velchevo -  4km<br/>\r\nAltitude: 200-299m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea size of Village of <strong>Pchelishte</strong>: 33km2<br/>\r\nPost code: 5048<br/>\r\nLatitude: 43.033N Longitude: 25.717E<br/>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Pchelishte</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Pchelishte - Hide\" /> </span></div>\r\n', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-pchelishte/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(192, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-samovodene', 'Property in Samovodene - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Samovodene property for sale, buy properties in Samovodene', 'Property in Samovodene - All the latest properties for sale in Samovodene | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Samovodene - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>Samovodene is a well developed village with a good infrastructure - View all the latest property for sale in the village</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Situated between the Kobilitsa and Byalata prast hills and dissected by the main E-85 road to Ruse, Samovodene is one of the largest villages in the region.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Samovodene</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Samovodene property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Covering around 42km2, it has a population of approximately 1700 inhabitants.  It is a popular village for permanent residence because of its close proximity to the main towns of <strong>Veliko Tarnovo</strong> and <strong>Gorna Oryahovitsa</strong>. The proximity of the Yantra River and River Rakovets, provides good conditions for development of fishing tourism<br/><br/>\r\nThe village of <strong>Samovodene</strong> offers a school and nursery, community centre, church, several shops, a general practitioner and a dentist. There are regular bus and taxi services into Veliko Tarnovo and other neighbouring villages as well as a train station.<br/><br/>\r\nA cultural landmark in the village is a 