(193, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-shemshevo', 'Property in Shemshevo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Shemshevo property for sale, buy properties in Shemshevo', 'Property in Shemshevo - All the latest properties for sale in Shemshevo | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Shemshevo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The area around Shemshevo is excellent for recreation and recuperation - View all the latest property for sale in this village</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">With its close proximity to the Western Industrial zone of Veliko Tarnovo, the area around Shemshevo is highly sought after by for investment.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Shemshevo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Shemshevo property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">The village of <strong>Shemshevo</strong> is situated 9 km west from the old capital of Bulgaria and 4 km away from the main arterial road Sofia – Varna. Due to its closeness to <strong>Veliko Tarnovo</strong> the settlement is perceived as a neighbourhood of the town; this makes it a much sought after area for people who are looking for a rural home with a nice garden that is in immediate proximity to a larger town. There are many young families with children living in the village. <strong>Shemshevo</strong> also attracts many people from Veliko Tarnovo and foreigners who are enchanted with the beautiful Bulgarian nature.<br/><br/>\r\n<strong>Shemshevo</strong> is set on the left bank of Yantra River. It is a