(194, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-sheremetya', 'Property in Sheremetya - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Sheremetya property for sale, buy properties in Sheremetya', 'Property in Sheremetya - All the latest properties for sale in Sheremetya | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Sheremetya - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The village of Sheremetya is intersected by the main arterial road Sofia – Varna and is just 5 km away from Veliko Tarnovo - View all the latest property for sale in this village</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Sheremetya was founded in 1688, initially at a different place, east of its present-day location. In 1870 the village was destroyed by fire and was rebuilt at its nowadays spot. The settlement reveals great views towards the Balkans Mountain.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Sheremetya</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Sheremetya property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Its prime location makes it a very lively village with lots of roadside restaurants, B&Bs and car dealerships.<br/><br/>\r\nThe village is well-developed, with good infrastructure. It has a village hall, community centre, pensioner’s club, new kids’ playground, monuments, and a renovated church. There is also a youth’s club.<br/><br/>\r\nThe region around <strong>Sheremetya</strong> abounds in Karst formations – caves, springs, hollows and others. Some of the places worth visiting in the area are Dupkata, Kovanlaka, Kisi Koriya, Baira, Uzundol and many