(195, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-tserova-koriya', 'Property in Tserova Koriya - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Tserova Koriya property for sale, buy properties in Tserova Koriya', 'Property in Tserova Koriya - All the latest properties for sale in Tserova Koriya | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Tserova Koriya - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Tserova Koriya &ndash; Veliko Tarnovo Municipality. The village of Tserova Koriya offers peace and quiet in a tranquil setting</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Tserova Koriya is a small village with an area of just 14 km2 and a population of approximately 500 inhabitants. <span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Tserova Koriya</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Tserova Koriya property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">The village in the centre of a valley between Veliko Tarnovo and the lower ridges of the Stara Planina.  North of the village lies the village of Dragizhevo, and to the south, the foothills of the mountains.   <strong>Tserova Koriya</strong> is one of the oldest settlements in the valley with the original inhabitants settling in the ancient Tserova forest, hence the name <strong>Tserova Koriya</strong>.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nIt is only 15km from the centre of Veliko Tarnovo making it extremely population for permanent living.  Amenities include shop, bars and cafes, a medical centre, post office, good internet/satellite/mobile reception and a regular bus service to nearby towns and villages.  The roads through <strong>Tserova Koriya</strong> are wide and asphalted, so access is available throughout the year. On the outskirts of the village there is a nature reserve, eco-trails for hiking and places suitable for lake and river fishing.<br /><br />\r\n\r\n<strong>Tserova Koriya</strong> is home to an elite winery producing wine for both the home market and for export.<br /><br /> Nearest Towns:  Veliko Tarnovo – 15km, Gorna Oryahovitsa – 13km, Lyaskovets – 9km<br />\r\nNearest Villages:  Pchelishte – 3km, Kapinovo – 6km, Dragizhevo – 4km<br />\r\nCoordinates: 43.033N, 25.75E<br />\r\nAltitude:  100-199m above sea level<br />\r\nArea Size: 14 km2<br />\r\nPostal Code: 5047<br />\r\n <span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Tserova Koriya</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Tserova Koriya - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-tserova-koriya/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(196, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-velchevo', 'Property in Velchevo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Velchevo property for sale, buy properties in Velchevo', 'Property in Velchevo - All the latest properties for sale in Velchevo | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Velchevo - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>Velchevo is a preferred location for recreation and relax due to its peacefulness and serenity.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\"><br /><strong>Velchevo</strong> is a village located in Veliko Tarnovo Municipality. Its name has been changed on several occasions during the years.\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Velchevo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"<strong>Velchevo</strong>elchevo property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">At its foundation it was named after the chiflik (farm) from which the settlement sprang to life. It later bore the name of the wife of Prince Regnant Ferdinand. Today its geographical denomination is connected to Velcho Dzhamdziyata, a prominent Bulgarian revolutionist.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nAlthough its name was changed the beautiful surroundings of the village of <strong>Velchevo</strong> have remained unspoiled through time. There are several guest houses in the region that welcome visitors throughout the year.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<strong>Velchevo</strong> has a library with a nice book collection and a community centre, with a museum exhibition presenting various items dating back from the foundation of the village and spa