(197, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-vetrintsi', 'Property in Vetrintsi - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Vetrintsi property for sale, buy properties in Velchevo', 'Property in Vetrintsi - All the latest properties for sale in Vetrintsi | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Vetrintsi - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The village of Vetrintsi is situated in a picturesque region.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\"><br /><strong>Vetrintsi</strong> It lays on both banks of Yantra River, which naturally separates the village in two parts – Gorna Mahala and Dolna Mahala (Upper Quarter and Lower Quarter).\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about Vetrintsi</span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Vetrintsi property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">This layout is what makes <strong>Vetrintsi</strong> an exceptionally beautiful place suitable for walks and relaxation within the nature and also for mountain biking. Don’t miss out the opportunity to sunbathe by Yantra River where you will be surprised by nice sandy banks.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nThe architecture of the old bridge spanning Yantra River at the village is very reminiscent of the work of the notable Bulgarian mason Kolyo Ficheto; there are also ancient fortress remains near the village.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<strong>Vetrintsi</strong> is located close to the main arterial road Sofia – Varna; a destination which makes it very suitable for a year round place of residence due to convenient transportation links to neighbouring villages and Veliko