(200, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-voneshta-voda', 'Property in Voneshta Voda - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Voneshta Voda property for sale, buy properties in Voneshta Voda', 'Property in Voneshta Voda - All the latest properties for sale inVoneshta Voda | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Voneshta Voda - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Voneshta Voda &ndash; Veliko Tarnovo Municipality</p>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-voneshta-voda/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(201, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-rusalya', 'Property in Rusalya - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Rusalya property for sale, buy properties in Rusalya', 'Property in Rusalya - All the latest properties for sale in Rusalya | Veliko Tarnovo', 'Property for sale in Rusalya - Veliko Tarnovo Municipality of North Bulgaria', '<p>View all the latest property for sale in the lovely village of Rusalya, set amongst beautiful rolling hills</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village is located approximately 20km north west of Veliko Tarnovo just off the main route between the towns of Veliko Tarnovo and Pavlikeni.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Rusalya</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Rusalya property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">With a population of around 500 inhabitants, Rusalya has all the basic amenities including a post office, grocers, restaurant, cafe and medical centre.  It has a modern infrastructure with good roads, mains water, electricity, landline and mobile connection and there is also a regular bus service to Veliko Tarnovo.<br/><br/>\r\nThe history tells that there were small villages in this area in the period of XII-XIV century, destroyed by conquerors. In XV century the area is inhabited again by Bulgarians and they established the village of Yalar, now called Rusalya village.<br/><br/>\r\nThe village has a river passing through it providing plenty of opportunities for fishing and there are Eco and rural tourism in the vicinity where you can go hiking or have a family picnic. Interesting places to visit near the village of Rusalya are the Cave, the Krali Marko stone and the Krali Marko foot print.<br/><br/>\r\nNearest Towns:  Veliko Tarnovo – 20km,  Pavlikeni – 15.8km<br/>\r\nNearest Villages:  Musina - 2.7km, Hotnitsa – 8.3km<br/>\r\nLatitude:  43.1669998<br/>\r\nLongtitude:  25.4500008<br/>\r\nAltitude: 126 m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea Size: 20.236km2<br/>\r\nPostal Code: 5057<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Rusalya</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Rusalya - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-rusalya/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(202, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-kereka', 'Property in Kereka - Dryanovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'kereka property for sale, buy properties in kereka', 'Property in Kereka - All the latest properties for sale in Kereka | Dryanovo', 'Property for sale in Kereka - Dryanovo municipality in the Gabrovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Kereka - A very popular village in the Municipality of Dryanovo</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Kereka village is situated in a small glen reminiscent of the Scottish glens which afford shelter to settlements in winter but provide magnificent views throughout the year. <span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Kereka</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Kereka property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Kereka, Kereca, Keraka, Керека</strong><br /><br /> Indeed <strong>Kereka</strong> affords such a status since the views of the Dryanovo Balkans are stunning, most houses in <strong>Kereka</strong> are fortunate enough to have one of these spectacular views. A little walk to the top of the hill provides you with views of the Stara Planina mountains and Mount Botev, where if lucky you can find a land plot in <strong>Kereka</strong> with these views and where you could build a new house in <strong>Kereka</strong> to behold these views day after day. The village of <strong>Kereka</strong> also benefits from shops and a small restaurant where you can have a drink and eat \"al fresco\" all day and well into the lovely warm evenings. <br /><br /> Please find below, a full list of the latest Property for sale in <strong>Kereka</strong>. <br /><br /> Nearest Town: Dryanovo 8km, Veliko Tarnovo 17km<br /> Nearest Village: Turkincha 3km, Balvantsite 4km, <br /> Altitude: 300 - 499m above sea level<br /> Area size of Village of <strong>Kereka</strong>: 11.936km2<br /> Post code: 5388<br /> Latitude: 43.033N Longitude: 25.467E<br /> <span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Kereka</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Kereka - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-kereka/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(203, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-dragizhevo', 'Property in Dragizhevo - Lyaskovets Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'dragizhevo property for sale, buy properties in dragizhevo', 'Property in Dragizhevo - All the latest properties for sale in Dragizhevo | Lyaskovets', 'Property for sale in Dragizhevo - Lyaskovets municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Dragizhevo - Close to Veliko Tarnovo in the Municipality of Lyaskovets</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Dragizhevo is blessed with having some beautiful views of the foothills of the Elena Balkan mountains and yet is only a 2 minute drive to the Varna - Sofia road.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Dragizhevo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Drag property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Dragizhevo, Dragijevo, Dragizevo, Dragezevo, Dragejevo, Dragezhevo, Dragichevo, Драгижево </strong><br /><br /> <strong>Dragizhevo</strong> originated as early as Neolithic times and then developed into a Slavic settlement and was mentioned in Ottoman documentation back in 1430. The highest hill above the village is Kosti myal whose top reaches 427 metres above sea level. If you walk to the top and look to the southeast will see a winding road to the village Tserova Koriya, Kapinovo and purple and dark blue peaks of the Elena Balkan mountains and to the east you can see Merdanya and Zlataritsa. To the north is the Lyaskovetz Petropalovski monastery which perches on top of the Arbanasi Plain overlooking the valley below and has been compared to a large white Eagle. <br /><br /> There is no doubt that the location makes it very popular and especially with foreigners looking to purchase a house in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong>. Furthermore, plots in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong> are popular too and this can be witnessed by seeing the development of Camping Veliko Tarnovo which now has a large camping plot in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong>, along  with a swimming pool, a shop which sells \"British\" food and goods, and a large house in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong> which commands fantastic views and hosts a bar, cafe and covered terrace where campers, guests and locals meet to eat and drink during the long hot Summers and warm Springs and Autumns, which are particularly mild in this part of Bulgaria. <br /><br /> <strong>Dragizhevo</strong> village centre has many bars and shops with a bus stop regularly serving the nearby market town of Gorna Oryahovitsa and Lyaskovets. Veliko Tarnovo is regularly serviced by buses as well. <br /><br /> The houses in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong> have large gardens as a rule and all face South in order to get the best out of the fertile soil, particularly vineyards which can be seen growing on plots in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong>. <br /><br /> Please find below, a full list of the latest Property for sale in <strong>Dragizhevo</strong>. <br /><br /> Nearest Town:  Lyaskovets 4km, Gorna Oryahovitsa 8km, Veliko Tarnovo 12km<br /> Nearest Village: Tserova Koriya 5km, Merdanya 5km <br /> Altitude: 200 - 299m above sea level<br /> Area size of Village of <strong>Dragizhevo</strong>: 16.823km2<br /> Post code: 5145<br /> Latitude: 43.067N Longitude: 25.733E<br /> <span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Dragizhevo</strong></span> <