(204, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-ganchovets', 'Property in Ganchovets - Dryanovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'ganchovets property for sale, buy properties in ganchovets', 'Property in Ganchovets - All the latest properties for sale in Ganchovets | Dryanovo', 'Property for sale in Ganchovets - Dryanovo municipality in the Gabrovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The small village of Ganchovets is nestled in the foothills of the Balkan Mountains, just 5 km away from Dryanovo and 21 km from Veliko Tarnovo</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village is situated near the main road Gabrovo-Veliko Tarnovo, which guarantees you an easy year round access.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Ganchovets</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Ganchovets property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Although the village has only 160 inhabitants, it is well developed. There are regular train transport to Drianovo, Veliko Tarnovo and the neighboring settlements. Ganchovets has electricity and water supply systems, a town hall, community center, two stores, a church and two guest houses.<br/><br/>\r\nEvery year in September in <strong>Ganchovets</strong> is organized Festival homemade brandy called \"Rakiya-magic.\" Besides \'Rakiya-Magic\' in the village regularly are organized cheerful events that attract both locals and tourists in the area.<br/><br/>\r\nOnly 11 km away is Drjanovski monastary \"St. Michael\" founded in the 12th century and the cave \"Bacho Kiro\", located west of the monastery, just 5 minutes walk. The cave was formed by the waters of the river and is Dryanovska maze with a total length of the galleries around 2,400 meters. Here goes eco trail, ideal for walking and relaxing holiday, in a unique scenery.<br/><br/>\r\nNear Ganchovets runs Dryanovska river, offering excellent fishing and beautiful surroundings provide opportunities for picnics and walks.<br/><br/>\r\nThe nearest town: Drianovo - 5 km, Veliko Tarnovo - 21 km, Gabrovo - 21 km<br/>\r\nThe nearest villages: Zaya - 2 km Salasuka - 2.7 km, Genya - 3.7 km<br/>\r\nArea size of Village of Ganchovets: 19,691 km2<br/>\r\nPostal Code: 5397<br/>\r\nAltitude: 289 m<br/>\r\nCoordinates: 42.988 ° N, 25.519 ° E<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Ganchovets</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Ganchovets - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-ganchovets/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(205, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-gostilitsa', 'Property in Gostilitsa - Dryanovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Gostilitsa property for sale, buy properties in Gostilitsa', 'Property in Gostilitsa - All the latest properties for sale in Gostilitsa | Dryanovo', 'Property for sale in Gostilitsa - Dryanovo municipality in the Gabrovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The mountain village of Gostilitsa offers fresh air, beautiful scenery in a most peaceful and quiet location</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Gostilitsa population is about 370 people, many of the inhabitants are foreigners from Western Europe and even Asia.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Gostilitsa</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Gostilitsa property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Gostilitsa is a mountain village is located in the breathtaking scenery of Dryanovski Balkan. The village is situated in a picturesque valley near Yantra River, 36 km. from Veliko Tarnovo, 15 km. from the town of Gabrovo. The area is rich in cultural and historical monuments. 2 km. south of the village there are interesting ruins of an old Roman fortress. The area offers opportunities for practicing sports such as hunting and fishing, and nature walks.<br/><br/>\r\nThe village has a town hall, shop, church, community center with a folk band and several guest houses. This function primary school, medical care is covered by a general practitioner. There is a regular bus service to Drianovo and neighboring settlements.<br/><br/>\r\n<strong>Gostilitsa</strong> village has historical records of almost two thousand years ago. And in the region are traced one of the first people who settled Europe. Household items and found bones in the cave \"Bacho Kiro\" Dryanovo monastery were left by prehistoric man lived before nearly 50,000 years. And this is only 3-4 km from the modern land of the village Gostilitsa. History of the village began in the second half of the 2nd c. AD. Two kilometers south of the present village in the \"fortress\" are the ruins of the old Roman Emporium called Diskoduratera. From the 15th century the village was known by his name Gostilitsa enshrined in old Turkish tax documents - for the first time in 1430 noted in Turkish as Gostildzha.<br/><br/>\r\nIn 1891 was built the church - \"Virgin Mary.\" And in 1894 the village was founded \"Hristo Botev\" community center, which in 1954 is housed in its own building, featuring a library, a spacious lounge and a modern stage, dressing rooms and others. There is manifested amateurs from the village folk songs and plays.<br/><br/>\r\nThe nearest cities: Drianovo - 13 km, Gabrovo 21,5 km, Veliko Tarnovo - 35 km<br/>\r\nThe nearest villages: Burya - 3.7 km, Slaveykovo - 4 km, Chukovo - 5 km<br/>\r\nArea size of Village of Gostilitsa: 32,404 km2<br/>\r\nPostal Code: 5390<br/>\r\nAltitude: 289 m<br/>\r\nCoordinates: 43.033 ° N, 25.367 ° E<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Gostilitsa</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Gostilitsa - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-gostilitsa/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(206, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-yantra', 'Property in Yantra - Dryanovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Yantra property for sale, buy properties in Yantra', 'Property in Yantra - All the latest properties for sale in Yantra | Dryanovo', 'Property for sale in Yantra - Dryanovo municipality in the Gabrovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Yantra - A popular village in the Municipality of Dryanovo - Gabrovo region</p>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-yantra/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(207, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-dlagnya', 'Property in Dlagnya - Dryanovo Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Dlagnya property for sale, buy properties in Dlagnya', 'Property in Dlagnya - All the latest properties for sale in Dlagnya | Dryanovo', 'Property for sale in Dlagnya - Dryanovo municipality in the Gabrovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>Dlagnya village is small, picturesque located in the Central Balkan Mountains, at the foot of the Gabrovo balkan</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The area offers stunning scenery, fresh mountain air, peace and quiet and offers the opportunity to enjoy a relaxing holiday.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Dlagnya</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Dlagnya property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Dlagnya is only about 10 minutes from Draynovo and 18 km. Veliko Tarnovo. The village is situated in a picturesque mountainous area and this makes it very attractive and a favourite place for rest and relaxation. Dlagnya is near the main road Veliko Tarnovo - Gabrovo, which guarantees you an easy year round access.<br/><br/>\r\n300 m. South of Dlagnya there was a large Roman settlement of I - II century. Another 100m. southwest there was a Roman fortress III - IV century. Within a radius of 2 km. around the village there are Thracian fortress I-II century BC. BC. and a large fortress II-nd Bulgarian Kingdom X - XIV century. And within a radius of 3-5 km. There are five ancient settlements.<br/><br/>\r\nBecause of its location <strong>Dlagnya</strong> was true renaissance