(268, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-Mihaltsi', 'Property in Mihaltsi - Pavlikeni Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'mihaltsi property for sale, buy properties in mihaltsi', 'Property in Mihaltsi - All the latest properties for sale in Mihaltsi | Pavlikeni', 'Property for sale in Mihaltsi - Pavlikeni municipality of Veliko Tarnovo', '<p>Mihaltsi is large and well developed village near a main road Sofia - Varna</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">It is located in a beautiful area offering lots of opportunities for relaxation and recreation.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Mihaltsi</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Mihaltsi property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Mihaltsi is one of the larger villages in Veliko Tarnovo Municipality; it is well-developed and has all the necessary amenities. There are a church, a town hall, a post office, an elementary school, a community centre and general stores. There is also a football pitch and an interesting airplane monument in the centre of the village. The settlement is located close to the main arterial road Sofia – Varna and 30 min away from Veliko Tarnovo; these facts render <strong>Mihaltsi</strong> a lively and desirable village. Locals are friendly and welcoming; the population of the village is around 1000 people.<br/><br/>\r\nBroom making was a popular way of earning one’s living but nowadays there are only few broom craftsmen left in Mihaltsi. The village is close to the Emenska eco path (the first of its kind in Bulgaria) which goes along