(309, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-parvomaytsi', 'Property in Parvomaytsi - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'parvomaytsi property for sale, buy properties in parvomaytsi', 'Property in Parvomaytsi  - All the latest properties for sale in Parvomaytsi ', 'Property for sale in Parvomaytsi - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Parvomaytsi - the largest village in Veliko Tarnovo region</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village is the excellent place for your new home in a calm rural setting but at the same time at close proximity to the main district town of Veliko Tarnovo.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Parvomaytsi</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Parvomaytsi property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Parvomaytsi</strong> is a well-developed village with regular public transport and good infrastructure, one of the most attractive villages in Veliko Tarnovo region. <strong>Parvomaytsi</strong> offers shops, a kindergarten, an elementary school, a town hall, a community centre, 2 churches as well as a doctor’s office and a dentist’s office. The settlenment is located on the left bank of Yantra River, near the junction railway station of Gorna Oryahovitsa and 12 km away from Veliko Tarnovo. The population of the village is 2700 people.<br/><br/>\r\nThe first written information about the existence of the village is from 1347. The present day village of <strong>Parvomaytsi</strong> was founded in 1955 when the two smaller villages of Temnichko and Sergyuvche were merged into one. The village boasts with a stone bridge built in 1884. It was designed by czech architects and who used as their inspiration the renowned Charles Bridge in Prague. The village is home to many successful enterprises – a lighting fixtures company, slaughter house, car repair garage, vehicle scrapyard. There are also many craftsmen like a currier and a cobbler.<br/><br/>\r\nNearest Town:  Gorna Oryahovitsa – 6 km, Lyaskovets – 9 km, Veliko Tarnovo – 16 km<br/>\r\nNearest Villages:  Samovodene – 5 km, Polikraishte – 5 km<br/>\r\nAltitude: 91 m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea size of Village of Merdanya: 32 km2<br/>\r\nPost code: 5139<br/>\r\nLatitude: 43.152 N Longitude: 25.650 Е<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Parvomaytsi</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Parvomaytsi - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-parvomaytsi /page-1', 'Desktop'),
(310, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-krusheto', 'Property in Krusheto - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'krusheto property for sale, buy properties in krusheto', 'Property in Krusheto  - All the latest properties for sale in Krusheto', 'Property for sale in Krusheto - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Krusheto - Great village, offering peace, tranquility and full relaxasation</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village Krushevo is a large and well established village in Northern Bulgaria.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Krusheto</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Krusheto property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">The village of <strong>Krusheto</strong> is 19 km away from Gorna Oryahovitsa and 25 km northeast of Veliko Tarnovo. Near the village passes the railway line and about 5 km west European route E85 passes. There is regular bus transport to and from the village.<br/><br/>\r\nThe first writen information for the village is from the late 17th century, when it was mentioned in a Turkish register. In 1880the village got its bulgarian name <strong>Krusheto</strong>. In 1884 was completed the construction of the church temple.<br/><br/> \r\nThe village is well developed with excellent infrastructure. <strong>Krusheto</strong> offers electrification, water supply system, partial sewerage system, telephone service, post office, internet and cable TV. The village has a town hall, primary school, kindergarten, community center, church and medical center.<br/><br/> \r\n<strong>Krusheto</strong> is located on the left bank of the River Rosica, which is suitable for fishing, hunting, recreation and walks in the beautiful scenery. Near the village are the remains of the ancient Roman town of Nicopolis ad Istrum and Kaleto with preserved walls. The complex is open from early spring to late autumn.<br/><br/>\r\nNearest towns: Gorna Oryahovitsa - 19 km, Polish Trumbesh - 18 km, Veliko Tarnovo - 25 km<br/>\r\nThe nearest villages: Kutsina - 6.6 km Nikyup - 7.5 km<br/>\r\nLand: 17,818 km2<br/>\r\nPostal Code: 5134<br/>\r\nAltitude: 147 m<br/>\r\nCoordinates: 43.233 N, 25.667 E<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Krusheto</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Krusheto - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-krusheto/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(311, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-polikraishte', 'Property in Polikraishte - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'polikraishte property for sale, buy properties in polikraishte', 'Property in Polikraishte - All the latest properties for sale in Polikraishte ', 'Property for sale in Polikraishte - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Polikraishte - one of the largest and most developed villages in Veliko Tarnovo</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village offers all the amenities for both holiday homes and permanent living.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Polikraishte</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Polikraishte property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Polikraishte</strong> is situated in a beautiful valley 3 km. from the south bank of the River Rositsa and 15 km. from Veliko Tarnovo. Its proximity to the old capital guarantee you that you can enjoy the pleasures that big town is offering.<br/><br/>\r\nThe village is lively, well developed, offers bus service to nearby towns, mobile coverage, post office, police office, shops and cafes, cable TV, pharmacy and school. The accsses to the village is quick and convenient - on the main road Ruse-Veliko Tarnovo. The proximity of the River Rosica give oportunities for fishing, walking, hiking and relaxing holiday in the beautiful scenery.<br/><br/>\r\n<strong>Polikraishte</strong> is one of the oldest settlements in the area. It was first mentioned in Turkish documents from the 15th century with the name Bulikraishte, and in 1618 was recorded as <strong>Polikraishte</strong>. Beginning of this village can be connected with the settlement of the Slavs. Four kilometers north of the village is the ancient Roman town of <strong>Nicopolis ad Instrum</strong>. In the settlement were discovered tomb mound, and various archaeological finds from Thracian times, suggesting occupancy by the Thracian.<br/><br/>\r\nIn 1751 a church was built in the village, which was dug into the ground. After liberation was demolished and in its place was built a new one. Attractions in the village of <strong>Polikraishte</strong> are: Clock Tower in the center of the village, the Orthodox Church \"St. Marina \", orthodox chapel \" St. Nikolai \". In the comunity center \"Razvitie\" - founded in 1884, are developing many different activities like female choir, group for authentic folklore and urban songs, children\'s dance group, and a group of folk customs. The library in the comunity center has over 14,500 volumes of different literature.<br/><br/>\r\nNearest Town:  Gorna Oryahovitsa – 9 km, Lyaskovets – 12 km, Veliko Tarnovo – 15 km<br/>\r\nNearest Villages:  Samovodene – 5 km, Krusheto – 5 km<br/>\r\nAltitude: 89 m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea size of Village of Polikraishte: 32,739 km2<br/>\r\nPost code: 5138<br/>\r\nLatitude: 43.183 N Longitude: 25.617 Е<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Polikraishte</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Polikraishte - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-polikraishte /page-1', 'Desktop');
