(312, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-draganovo', 'Property in Draganovo - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'draganovo property for sale, buy properties in draganovo', 'Property in Draganovo - All the latest properties for sale in Draganovo', 'Property for sale in Draganovo - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Draganovo - a village that tempts with the excellent living conditions it provides</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Due to its good infrastructure, peacefulness and close proximity to the town of Veliko Tarnovo, the village is a much preferred place both for a permanent residence and for vacations.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Draganovo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Draganovo property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\"><strong>Draganovo</strong> is a large and well-developed village, situated close to the banks of Yantra River, just 15 km north of Gorna Oryahovitsa. The village has good infrastructure and all the necessary amenities such as cafes, shops, a restaurant, a pharmacy, a doctor’s office, post office, community centre and gas station. There is also regular public transport to neighbouring towns and villages. <strong>Draganovo</strong> also benefits from a kindergarten and elementary school. Its population is 2700 people.<br/><br/>\r\nThe main means of living for the locals are agriculture and stock breeding. The village boasts with several landmarks worth seeing, namely The Clock Tower erected with funds donated by locals who are working abroad; the Monument of the Workers’ International – unique in its kind in Bulgaria; the Asen Raztsvetnikov Historic House Museum where you will find an exposition of many of the writer’ personal belongings and the Monument of the people of <strong>Draganovo</strong> who died in the Balkan Wars and in the First World War. The village is also good for relaxation – the river running through it is the ideal place for fishing, sun bathing and family picnics and the near forest is great for hiking.<br/><br/>\r\nNearest Town:  Lyaskovets – 14 km, Gorna Oryahovitsa – 15 km, Veliko Tarnovo – 26 km<br/>\r\nNearest Villages:  Yantra – 8 km, Polikraishte – 13 km, Sushitsa – 15 km<br/>\r\nAltitude: 50 - 99 m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea size of the village: 62 km2<br/>\r\nPost code: 5137<br/>\r\nLatitude: 43.216 N Longitude: 25.750 Е<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Draganovo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Draganovo - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-draganovo/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(313, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-gorski-dolen-trambesh', 'Property in Gorski Dolen Trambesh - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'gorski dolen trambesh property for sale, buy properties in gorski dolen trambesh', 'Property in Gorski Dolen Trambesh - All the latest properties for sale in Gorski Dolen Trambesh', 'Property for sale in Gorski Dolen Trambesh - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Gorski Dolen Trambesh - a Picturesque village situated near Yantra River</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village of Gorski Dolen Trambesh is small but well developed. <span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Gorski Dolen Trambesh</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Gorski Dolen Trambesh property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">It has shops, pubs, community center and church. There is a regular bus service to the nearby towns and villages. There are excellent conditions for the development of rural tourism and fishing tourism due to the proximity of the Yantra River.<br/><br/>\r\nVillage of <strong>Gorski Dolen Trambesh</strong> is located 18 km northeast ofGorna Oryahovitsa. The village offers panoramic views as it is located on the southern slope of the Kaleto area. From here you have a great veiw of the river valleys of Yantra and Lefedzha (Old River) and as well as other villages in the municipality (Vurbitsa, Pisarevo, Draganovo, Lower Oriahovitsa).<br/><br/>\r\nThe fertile lands located along the two rivers (Yantra and Lefedzha) help the settelment of the territory. Today in <strong>Gorski Dolen Trambesh</strong> live around 350 inhabitants. In the village of <strong>Gorski Dolen Trambesh</strong> is the largest vineyard (500 acres) in the municipality of Gorna Oryahovitsa planted with dessert (Bolgar) and wine (Aligote and Rkatziteli) varieties.<br/><br/>\r\nThe nearest cities: Gorna Oryahovitsa - 20 km, Strazhitsa - 23 km<br/>\r\nThe nearest villages: Gorski Goren Trambesh - 5.5 km Draganovo - 8 km, Varbitsa - 5 km<br/>\r\nLand: 12,766 km2<br/>\r\nPostal Code: 5131<br/>\r\nAltitude: 57 meters above sea level<br/>\r\nCoordinates: 43.2 N, 25.85 E<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Gorski Dolen Trambesh</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Gorski Dolen Trambesh - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-gorski-dolen-trambesh/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(314, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-pisarevo', 'Property in Pisarevo - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'pisarevo property for sale, buy properties in pisarevo', 'Property in Pisarevo - All the latest properties for sale in Polikraishte ', 'Property for sale in Pisarevo - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Pisarevo - The beautiful nature and the peace and tranquillity of the region render Pisarevo and the vicinity a desired location away from the hustle and bustle of big towns.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The proximity to Veliko Tarnovo and the picturesque location make Pisarevo a village suitable both for a permanent home and a vacation destination.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Pisarevo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Pisarevo property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">The village of <strong>Pisarevo</strong> is situated 10 km away from Gorna Oryahovitsa and 22 km away from Veliko Tarnovo. The village is large, with good infrastructure. <strong>Pisarevo</strong> has shops, a town hall, restaurant, church, mosque, community centre and pensioners’ club and provides regular public transport to neighbouring towns and villages. There are also an elementary school and a kindergarten. The population of the settlement is 1200 people.<br/><br/>\r\nThe first written information about the existence of the village dates back to Roman times. <strong>Pisarevo</strong> changed its location three times during the years. It also altered its name; its present days name is said to come from the professional occupation of a Bulgarian who used to do the accounting of the local village master. The main means of living of the population are agriculture, stock breeding and gardening. The village also hosts an annual festival of the authentic Bulgarian folk music. Yantra River runs nearby providing excellent recreational opportunities such as fishing, family day outs and sun bathing.<br/><br/>\r\nNearest Town:  Dolna Oryahovitsa – 5 km, Lyaskovets – 10 km, Gorna Oryahovitsa – 11 km, Veliko Tarnovo – 23 km<br/>\r\nNearest Villages:  Varbitsa – 4 km, Gorski Dolen Trambesh – 9 km, Draganovo – 12 km<br/>\r\nAltitude: 100 - 199 m above sea level<br/>\r\nArea size of the village: 11 km2<br/>\r\nPost code: 5127<br/>\r\nLatitude: 43.150 N Longitude: 25.783Е<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>Pisarevo</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"Pisarevo - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/latest-property-pisarevo/page-1', 'Desktop'),
(315, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-pravda', 'Property in Pravda - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'pravda property for sale, buy properties in pravda', 'Property in Pravda - All the latest properties for sale in Pravda ', 'Property for sale in Pravda - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Pravda - The village of Pravda has lovely climate conditions and offers the peace and tranquillity you will not find in the big city</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The beautiful nature and the close proximity of Veliko Tarnovo make Pravda an excellent choice for your new home.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Pravda<strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Pravda property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">The village of <strong>Pravda</strong> is nice and peaceful, not too big, but well-developed. It boasts with asphalt street, central sewerage, shops and regular bus transport and all the necessary amenities for a good way of life in the countryside. The village also has a railway station, part of the Gorna Oryahovitsa – Ruse route. <strong>Pravda</strong> has great climate and fertile soil and is very beneficial for growing vegetables, fruit and grain crops. The population of the settlement is around 600 people.<br/><br/>\r\nThe first written information about the existence of the village is from 1415. Near <strong>Pravda</strong> were discovered remains of settlement dated back to the Neolithic period. Many ceramic and f