(318, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-gorski-goren-trambesh', 'Property in Gorski Goren Trambesh - Gorna Oryahovitsa Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'gorski goren trambesh property for sale, buy properties in gorski goren trambesh', 'Property in Gorski Goren Trambesh - All the latest properties for sale in Gorski Goren Trambesh', 'Property for sale in Gorski Goren Trambesh - Gorna Oryahovitsa municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The very latest property for sale in Gorski Goren Trambesh - Small village located a kilometer away from the river Yantra</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Village of Gorski Goren Trambesh is located in predbalkansnite hills of Stara Planina.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Gorski Goren Trambesh</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Gorski Goren Trambesh property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Gorski Goren Trambesh is located 305 meters above sea level and is one of the highest settlements in the municipality of Gorna Oryahovitsa.<br/><br/> \r\nThe village is small, with a population of about 170 people, but is well developed. There are shop, pub, retirement home, community center and church. There is a regular bus service to and from Gorna Oriahovitsa and neighboring villages. In the village there are more than 20 fountains. The main occupation in the village is agriculture. There are excellent conditions for the development of both rural and fishing tourism, due to the proximity of the Yantra River.<br/><br/>\r\nIn Gorski Goren Trambesh people can se