(372, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-donkovtsi', 'Property in Donkovtsi - Elena Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Donkovtsi property for sale, buy properties in Donkovtsi', 'Property in Donkovtsi- All the latest properties for sale in Donkovtsi | Elena', 'Property for sale in Donkovtsi - Elena municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>Donkovtsi is a small mountain village located just 10 min. from Elena town</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village offers panoramic views towards the Stara Planina, Elena and Yovkovtsi dam.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Donkovtsi</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Donkovtsi property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Donkovtsi village is located near the bridge over the dam Yovkovtsi, which is one of the largest in Bulgaria. You will have the opportunity to enjoy the fresh air, serene atmosphere and beautiful scenery of the Elena Balkan.<br/><br/>  \r\nThe village of Donkovtsi is suitable for permanent living, as it is located near the town of Elena. It is also suitable for holiday, as the area offers beautiful mountain scenery, fresh air and it’s a good place for fishing, hunting and rural tourism.<br/><br/> \r\nYovkovtsi dam offers excellent opportunities for fishing, sunbathing and picnics. For avid travellers here date back to different hiking trails, some of which end in Chumerna pick. The large reservoir and the appropriate altitude make the area of the village <strong>Donkovtsi</strong> suitable for treating lung problems.<br/><br/>\r\nT