(382, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'latest-property-badevtsi', 'Property in Badevtsi - Elena Municipality Bulgaria | Yantra Homes', 'Badevtsi property for sale, buy properties in Badevtsi', 'Property in Badevtsi- All the latest properties for sale in Badevtsi | Elena', 'Property for sale in Badevtsi - Elena municipality in the Veliko Tarnovo Region of North Bulgaria', '<p>The small mountain village of Badevtsi is situated in Elena Balkan, near dam Yovkovtsi and the town of Elena</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">The village has a rich history dating back to the Romans and Thracians.<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>Badevtsi</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Badevtsi property &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">Badevtsi village is located 20 km. from the town of Elena and 32 km. Veliko Tarnovo. It is situated in quiet rural area easily accessible all year round and close to all amenities. In Badevtsi there are electricity and water supply systems, and GSM coverage. The village has a community centre, founded in 1942. The village offers excellent opportunities for recreation and entertainment among the fresh air, pure mountain scenery and relaxed atmosphere.<br/><br/>\r\nThe village is close to the dam \"Yovkovtsi\" which offers excellent fishing conditions and provides opportunities for fishing tourism. There is a very good tourist infrastructure. The place is suitable for vacations close to nature and practicing water motor sports, also nearby and horse riding.<br/><br/>\r\nThe houses in the village are picturesquely located on