(472, 'en', 'fast-search-results', 'houses-for-sale-with-pool', 'Houses for Sale with Swimming Pools: Find Your Dream Home in Bulgaria', 'Houses for sale with swimming pool, for sale houses with pool', 'Discover the allure of Bulgarian properties for sale with swimming pools. Enjoy endless summer relaxation and lucrative investment potential in your own private oasis', 'Houses for sale with a swimming pool', '<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0;\">Private swimming pools have become a popular feature in the Bulagrian property market. The favourable weather in Bulgaria allows you to use a pool throughout the long, hot summer months that usually last well into the autumn. Properties featuring outdoor swimming pools have higher rental appeal and can add significant value to a property, making them an excellent investment.<br/>\r\n\r\n<span id=\"link_view\" class=\"clear_l pointer f_right mt_5px\" style=\"display: block;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_hide\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Read more about <strong>houses for sale with swimming pools</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_down.png\" alt=\"Bulgarian houses for sale with pool &ndash; Read More\" /> </span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"text_more\" class=\"clear_l mt_10px display_none fs_13px a_justify \" style=\"width: 672px; color: #4a4a4a; display: none;\">\r\n\r\n<h2>Swimming Pool Homes for Sale: Our latest list of houses with a pool</h2>\r\nOur most recent list of properties with pools for sale is provided below. These swimming pool homes offer the ideal opportunity to enjoy all the benefits of having your own private oasis without having to travel. From refreshing morning dips to evening relaxation, these properties offer the perfect retreat for those seeking a luxurious lifestyle. Don\'t miss out on the opportunity to own a home with a pool and enjoy the ultimate comfort and convenience it brings, provided by homes for sale with swimming pools. There is certain to be something that suits your needs and budget, given the wide variety of styles and sizes available.<br/><br/>\r\n<h2>Option two: Buy a house that has a big enough land for you to construct a swimming pool.</h2>\r\nAnother option is to buy a property that has enough land to build your own pool. When planning to build your own swimming pool, there are several important considerations to keep in mind. Here are some key factors to consider:<br/><br/>\r\n<strong>Location:</strong> Choose a suitable location for your pool. Consider factors such as the terrain; the construction of a pool on rocky ground is considerably more expensive than if it is on soft earth. Other considerations are sun exposure, privacy, accessibility, and the impact on existing structures, utility lines, and trees. Assess any potential risks, such as groundwater levels or flood-prone areas.<br/><br/>\r\n<strong>Planning Regulations:</strong> It is important to comply with local regulations and permits required for constructing a pool. The construction of any new pool requires permission. The required permission is minimal for pools up to 100 cubic metres. The regulations become more detailed if the pool is larger than this. There are a number of specialist pool companies in the area that can give more detailed advice about planning permission.<br/><br/>\r\n<strong>Water source:</strong> In the areas of Veliko Tarnovo and Gabrovo, numerous properties have their own water source. This could take the shape of a borehole or a water well. The cost of filling a pool from the public water system can be high, and there might be limits on how much water can be used during the summer. Having your own water source can be an excellent solution to those problems.<br/><br/>\r\n<h2>Factors to Consider When Buying a House with a Swimming Pool</h2>\r\nCheck the condition of the pool and its equipment before buying.\r\nBefore buying a house with a swimming pool, it is important to check the condition of the pool and its equipment. A thorough inspection should be done to ensure that there are no leaks or cracks in the pool\'s structure. It is also important to check that all of the equipment, such as pumps and filters, are in good working condition.<br/><br/>\r\nIf there are any issues with the pool or its equipment, it is important to factor these costs into your decision-making process. Repairing or replacing a pool can be expensive, so it is best to know what you\'re getting into before making an offer on a house with a swimming pool.<br/><br/>\r\n<h2>Think about safety measures.</h2>\r\nSwimming pools can be dangerous, especially for children. That\'s why it\'s essential to consider safety measures when buying a house with a swimming pool. This may include installing fencing around the pool area, using covers when not in use, and installing alarms that sound if someone enters the water without supervision.<br/><br/>\r\n<h2>Dive into your own Luxury: Houses for Sale with Private Swimming Pools in Bulgaria</h2>\r\nOwning a house with a swimming pool can be an excellent investment for many reasons. Firstly, it provides you with a variety of options within your budget, from dream homes to luxury properties that come equipped with swimming pools. Secondly, if you have always dreamed of owning a home with a pool, then buying a property with enough land to build one could be the perfect solution.<br/><br/>\r\nHowever, before taking the plunge and investing in a house with a swimming pool, there are several factors to consider. You need to think about the type of pool you want and its maintenance costs. You should also consider how much time and effort will go into maintaining your new pool.<br/><br/>\r\n<h2>Why Buying a House with a Swimming Pool is Worth It</h2>\r\nDespite these considerations, purchasing a home with a swimming pool is worth it for many reasons. For starters, it adds value to your property while also providing an excellent place for relaxation and entertainment during the hot summer months. Moreover, having access to your own private oasis can provide numerous health benefits, such as reducing stress levels and improving overall fitness.<br/><br/>\r\nFurthermore, owning a house with a swimming pool allows you to create unforgettable memories with family and friends. Whether hosting barbeques or throwing birthday parties for kids, your garden becomes the ultimate gathering spot when equipped with this luxurious amenity.<br/>\r\n<span id=\"link_hide\" class=\"clear_l pointer mt_5px f_right display_none\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"$(\'div#text_more\').slideToggle(); $(this).hide(); $(\'span#link_view\').show();\"> <span class=\"link\">Hide information about <strong>houses for sale with pool</strong></span> <img style=\"display: inline; float: none; width: 8px;\" src=\"application/images/arrow_up.png\" alt=\"for sale houses with pool - Hide\" /> </span></div>', 'www.yantrahomes.co.uk/en/fast-search-results/houses-for-sale-with-pool/page-1', 'Desktop'),
